reviewText: Swell story idea , GREAT dialog and excellent performances all ad up to an above average film that will leave you smiling . Lee Bowman is a new actor/face to me but fully holds his own with an great ensemble of seasoned pros . Terrific .
George Macreepy in one of his signature bad dudes,masquerading as a missionary,unlike his good guy preacher in Alias Nick Beal. One good film is all I can say. Highly recommend movie & vendor.
